Global IP Geo-Location Service Market Insights
IP Geo-Location Service Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 18.2% from 2024 to 2030.

IP Geo-Location Service Market Overview
The IP Geo-Location Service Market has been experiencing substantial growth due to the rising demand for location-based services. As of 2025, the global market value is estimated to reach USD 4.5 billion, with a significant CAGR of 15.3% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is attributed to the increasing adoption of e-commerce, personalized advertising, and the surge in mobile internet usage. IP Geo-Location technology helps businesses provide localized content, enhance customer experience, and improve fraud detection, driving its widespread application across industries such as retail, travel, and finance.

